						<summary>

						<p>Wall of the Veṅkaṭēśvarasvāmi temple.</p>						

						<p>This is dated <hi rend="bold">Śaka 1528, Parābhava, Āshāḍha ba. 2</hi> corresponding to 1606 A.D., July 11, Friday.</p>						

						<p>Damaged. It records a grant probably of land by a <hi rend="italic">kāryakartta</hi> (name lost) of Maṭli Tiruveṅgaḷanātha Dēvachōḍa Mahārāju to the <hi rend="italic">kāṁpus</hi> and the <hi rend="italic">karaṇas</hi> of Gaṅganapalle.</p>						

						</summary>
